  "def": "$S_{agency} = (Spectrum_{control}, Level_{current}, Sens_{ctx}, Adj_{dynamic}) : Context \\to Control_{distribution}$",
  "desc": "Peer-to-peer architecture pattern enables direct communication between nodes without central coordination.",
  "comps": [
